--ACTIVE MEMBERS SELECT PA.*,PER.*,P.*,PE.*,PED.*,ORG.*,PAG.*,PAPE.* FROM ( SELECT PED.*,PAED.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID , ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY PAED.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID ORDER BY ISNULL(PED.END_DATE,'01/01/2900') DESC,ISNULL(PE.END_DATE,'01/01/2900') DESC, PED.START_DATE DESC , PE.START_DATE DESC, PED.PERSON_EMPLOYMENT_DTL_ID DESC ) AS ROWRANK FROM SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_EMPLOYMENT_DETAIL PAED(NOLOCK) INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON_EMPLOYMENT_DETAIL PED(NOLOCK) ON PAED.PERSON_EMPLOYMENT_DTL_ID = PED.PERSON_EMPLOYMENT_DTL_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON_EMPLOYMENT PE(NOLOCK) ON PE.PERSON_EMPLOYMENT_ID = PED.PERSON_EMPLOYMENT_ID WHERE @HISTORY_DATE BETWEEN PED.START_DATE AND DATEADD(M,1,ISNULL(PED.END_DATE,'01/01/2900')) AND @HISTORY_DATE BETWEEN LEFT(CONVERT(CHAR(8),DATEADD(M,1, PE.START_DATE), 111),8) + '01' AND DATEADD(M,1,ISNULL(PE.END_DATE,'01/01/2900')) AND PAED.ELECTION_VALUE = 'ENLD'
) AS PED INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT PA(NOLOCK) ON PA.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID = PED.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID AND PED.ROWRANK = 1 INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON_EMPLOYMENT PE ON PED.PERSON_EMPLOYMENT_ID = PE.PERSON_EMPLOYMENT_ID INNER JOIN SGT_ORGANIZATION ORG(NOLOCK) ON ORG.ORG_ID = PE.ORG_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PLAN P(NOLOCK) ON P.PLAN_ID = PA.PLAN_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON PER(NOLOCK) ON PER.PERSON_ID = PA.PERSON_ID LEFT JOIN ( SELECT PAG.* FROM SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_GHDV PAG(NOLOCK) INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_GHDV_HISTORY PAGH WITH(NOLOCK) ON PAG.PERSON_ACCOUNT_GHDV_ID = PAGH.PERSON_ACCOUNT_GHDV_ID WHERE PAGH.PLAN_PARTICIPATION_STATUS_VALUE = 'ENL2' AND (PAGH.HEALTH_INSURANCE_TYPE_VALUE IS NULL OR PAGH.HEALTH_INSURANCE_TYPE_VALUE NOT IN('RT09','RT12')) AND PAGH.COBRA_TYPE_VALUE IS NULL AND @HISTORY_DATE BETWEEN PAGH.START_DATE AND ISNULL(PAGH.END_DATE,'01/01/2900') AND PAGH.START_DATE <> CASE WHEN PAGH.END_DATE IS NOT NULL THEN PAGH.END_DATE ELSE '01/01/2900' END AND (@HEALTH_INSURANCE_TYPE = '' OR PAGH.HEALTH_INSURANCE_TYPE_VALUE = @HEALTH_INSURANCE_TYPE) AND @HISTORY_DATE BETWEEN PAGH.START_DATE AND ISNULL(PAGH.END_DATE,'01/01/2900') AND (@COVERAGE_CODE = '' OR PAGH.COVERAGE_CODE = @COVERAGE_CODE) ) PAG ON PAG.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID = PA.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID LEFT JOIN SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_PAYMENT_ELECTION PAPE WITH (NOLOCK) ON PA.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID = PAPE.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID WHERE P.PLAN_ID = 12 AND (PA.START_DATE >= @START_DATE) AND (ISNULL(PA.END_DATE,'01/01/2900') <= @END_DATE) AND PAG.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID IS NOT NULL AND (@PERSON_ID = 0 OR PA.PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID) AND (@ORG_ID = 0 OR PE.ORG_ID=@ORG_ID)

--RGROUP MEMBERS SELECT PA.*,P.*,PL.*,PAG.*,ORG.*,PAPE.* FROM SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT PA WITH (NOLOCK) INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_PAYMENT_ELECTION PAPE WITH (NOLOCK) ON PA.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID = PAPE.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON P WITH (NOLOCK) ON PA.PERSON_ID= P.PERSON_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PLAN PL WITH (NOLOCK) ON PA.PLAN_ID = PL.PLAN_ID LEFT JOIN SGT_ORGANIZATION ORG ON ORG.ORG_ID=PAPE.IBS_ORG_ID LEFT JOIN ( SELECT PAG.* FROM SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_GHDV PAG(NOLOCK) INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_GHDV_HISTORY PAGH WITH(NOLOCK) ON PAG.PERSON_ACCOUNT_GHDV_ID = PAGH.PERSON_ACCOUNT_GHDV_ID WHERE PAGH.PLAN_PARTICIPATION_STATUS_VALUE = 'ENL2' AND (@HEALTH_INSURANCE_TYPE = '' OR PAGH.HEALTH_INSURANCE_TYPE_VALUE = @HEALTH_INSURANCE_TYPE) AND (@COVERAGE_CODE = '' OR PAGH.COVERAGE_CODE = @COVERAGE_CODE) AND @HISTORY_DATE BETWEEN PAGH.START_DATE AND ISNULL(PAGH.END_DATE,'01/01/2900') AND PAGH.START_DATE <> CASE WHEN PAGH.END_DATE IS NOT NULL THEN PAGH.END_DATE ELSE '01/01/2900' END ) PAG ON PAG.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID = PA.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID WHERE PL.PLAN_ID=12 AND (IBS_ORG_ID IS NOT NULL OR IBS_SUPPLEMENTAL_ORG_ID IS NOT NULL) AND PAPE.IBS_EFFECTIVE_DATE <= @HISTORY_DATE AND PAG.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID IS NOT NULL AND (PA.START_DATE >= @START_DATE) AND (ISNULL(PA.END_DATE,'01/01/2900') <= @END_DATE) AND (@PERSON_ID = 0 OR PA.PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID) AND (@ORG_ID = 0 OR PAPE.IBS_ORG_ID=@ORG_ID)

--IBS Members SELECT PA.*,P.*,PL.*,PAG.*,PAPE.* FROM SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT PA WITH (NOLOCK) INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_PAYMENT_ELECTION PAPE WITH (NOLOCK) ON PA.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID = PAPE.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON P WITH (NOLOCK) ON PA.PERSON_ID= P.PERSON_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PLAN PL WITH (NOLOCK) ON PA.PLAN_ID = PL.PLAN_ID LEFT JOIN ( SELECT PAG.* FROM SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_GHDV PAG(NOLOCK) INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_GHDV_HISTORY PAGH WITH(NOLOCK) ON PAG.PERSON_ACCOUNT_GHDV_ID = PAGH.PERSON_ACCOUNT_GHDV_ID WHERE PAGH.PLAN_PARTICIPATION_STATUS_VALUE = 'ENL2' AND (PAGH.HEALTH_INSURANCE_TYPE_VALUE IN ('RT09','RT12') OR PAGH.COBRA_TYPE_VALUE IS NOT NULL) AND (@HEALTH_INSURANCE_TYPE = '' OR PAGH.HEALTH_INSURANCE_TYPE_VALUE = @HEALTH_INSURANCE_TYPE) AND (@COVERAGE_CODE = '' OR PAGH.COVERAGE_CODE = @COVERAGE_CODE) AND @HISTORY_DATE BETWEEN PAGH.START_DATE AND ISNULL(PAGH.END_DATE,'01/01/2900') AND PAGH.START_DATE <> CASE WHEN PAGH.END_DATE IS NOT NULL THEN PAGH.END_DATE ELSE '01/01/2900' END ) PAG ON PAG.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID = PA.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID WHERE PL.PLAN_ID=12 AND (PA.START_DATE >= @START_DATE) AND (ISNULL(PA.END_DATE,'01/01/2900') <= @END_DATE) AND IBS_FLAG = 'Y' AND (IBS_ORG_ID IS NULL OR (IBS_ORG_ID IS NOT NULL AND ISNULL(COBRA_EMPR_SHARE,0) > 0 AND ISNULL(COBRA_EMPR_SHARE,0) < 100)) AND PAPE.IBS_EFFECTIVE_DATE <= @HISTORY_DATE AND (@PERSON_ID = 0 OR PA.PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID) AND PAG.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID IS NOT NULL

-- I AM TAKING ALL THE HISTORY RECORDS HERE SINCE WE NEED TO GET THE HEALTH PARTICIPATION DATE FOR RETIREE BY -- WALKING THRU ALL THE HISTORY. SO, WE MUST LOAD ALL THE HISTORY. SELECT PAGH.* FROM SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT PA WITH (NOLOCK) INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_PAYMENT_ELECTION PAPE WITH (NOLOCK) ON PA.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID = PAPE.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_GHDV PAG(NOLOCK) ON PAG.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID = PA.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_GHDV_HISTORY PAGH(NOLOCK) ON PAGH.PERSON_ACCOUNT_GHDV_ID = PAG.PERSON_ACCOUNT_GHDV_ID WHERE PA.PLAN_ID =12 AND PAGH.START_DATE <= @BATCHDATE AND --IGNORE FUTURE DATED ENTRIES PAGH.START_DATE <> ISNULL(PAGH.END_DATE,'01/01/2900') AND --IGNORE SAME DATED HISTORY RECORDS (IBS_FLAG = 'Y' OR IBS_SUPPLEMENTAL_FLAG = 'Y') AND ((PA.PLAN_ID =12 AND (IBS_ORG_ID IS NULL OR (PA.PLAN_ID IN (9,12) AND IBS_ORG_ID IS NOT NULL AND ISNULL(COBRA_EMPR_SHARE,0) > 0 AND ISNULL(COBRA_EMPR_SHARE,0) < 100)) AND IBS_SUPPLEMENTAL_ORG_ID IS NULL) OR (PA.PLAN_ID = 13)) ORDER BY ISNULL(PAGH.END_DATE,'2900-01-01') DESC, PAGH.START_DATE DESC,PAGH.PERSON_ACCOUNT_GHDV_HISTORY_ID DESC

SELECT PAGH.* FROM SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_EMPLOYMENT_DETAIL PAED(NOLOCK) INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON_EMPLOYMENT_DETAIL PED(NOLOCK) ON PAED.PERSON_EMPLOYMENT_DTL_ID = PED.PERSON_EMPLOYMENT_DTL_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON_EMPLOYMENT PE(NOLOCK) ON PE.PERSON_EMPLOYMENT_ID = PED.PERSON_EMPLOYMENT_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT PA(NOLOCK) ON PA.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID = PAED.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_GHDV PAG(NOLOCK) ON PAG.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID = PA.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_GHDV_HISTORY PAGH(NOLOCK) ON PAGH.PERSON_ACCOUNT_GHDV_ID = PAG.PERSON_ACCOUNT_GHDV_ID WHERE PAED.ELECTION_VALUE = 'ENLD' AND PAGH.PLAN_PARTICIPATION_STATUS_VALUE = 'ENL2' AND (PAGH.DENTAL_INSURANCE_TYPE_VALUE IS NULL OR PAGH.DENTAL_INSURANCE_TYPE_VALUE <> 'RT16') AND (PAGH.HEALTH_INSURANCE_TYPE_VALUE IS NULL OR PAGH.HEALTH_INSURANCE_TYPE_VALUE NOT IN('RT09','RT12')) AND (PAGH.VISION_INSURANCE_TYPE_VALUE IS NULL OR PAGH.VISION_INSURANCE_TYPE_VALUE <> 'RETR') AND PAGH.COBRA_TYPE_VALUE IS NULL AND @PAYROLLPAIDDATE BETWEEN PAGH.START_DATE AND ISNULL(PAGH.END_DATE,'01/01/2900') AND PAGH.START_DATE <> ISNULL(PAGH.END_DATE,'01/01/2900') AND --IGNORE SAME DATED HISTORY RECORDS @PAYROLLPAIDDATE BETWEEN PED.START_DATE AND ISNULL(PED.END_DATE,'01/01/2900') AND @PAYROLLPAIDDATE BETWEEN PE.START_DATE AND ISNULL(PE.END_DATE,'01/01/2900') AND PAED.PLAN_ID =12 ORDER BY PAGH.PERSON_ACCOUNT_GHDV_HISTORY_ID DESC
SELECT * FROM SGT_ORG_PLAN WITH(NOLOCK) WHERE PLAN_ID=12
